description:
Hello, I'm Agatha! 😊

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching :)

I'm sorry if the video was a bit shaky 😅✌

In today's video, I'm going to do a chit chat get ready with me and also share with you the beauty trends this 2021. The look that I did for today's look was inspired by one of Gigi Hadid's makeup look which is a neutral brown makeup!

If you have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

article link 
https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/beauty-hair/beauty-trends/g14009805/big-makeup-trends/

Dasom Skincare Primer
The Saem tip concealer in 02
Vice Cosmetics Duo Finish Foundation in Putinamez
Vice Cosmetics Gandoll Volumizing Brow Gel in Ash Brown
Careline Best Brow Liner in Taupe
Eb Advance face trio in fig
Careline Shadow Palette in Dream Catcher
Maybelline Hyper Curl Mascara
Vice Cosmetics Aura Blush in Title
Wet and Wild MegaGlo Highlighter in Precious Petals
Detail Cosmetics Powder Pout in Ry Velasco
Vice Cosmetics Good Vibes Matte Lipstick in Ganderz


Let's be friends!
